'''任务中失踪'''（{{lang-en|Missing in action；MIA}}）是军事损失的一种，指的是军事人员在战斗行动中被上报失踪。他们的结局有可能是战死、受伤、被俘或者逃跑。对于战死者来说，其遗体或坟墓在没有得到确认的情况下才算失踪。在战争的历史中，任务中失踪一直是军事人员面临的很大的风险。

==二战==
[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]中有大批的军人失踪。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www2.hs.fi/english/archive/news.asp?id=20021022IE19 |title=hs.fi |publisher=.hs.fi |accessdate=November 14, 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629165259/http://www2.hs.fi/english/archive/news.asp?id=20021022IE19 |archivedate=2011年6月29日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.defenselink.mil/releases/release.aspx?releaseid=10170 |title=defenselink.mil |publisher=defenselink.mil |accessdate=November 14, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091201002711/http://www.defenselink.mil/releases/release.aspx?releaseid=10170 |archive-date=2009-12-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.raf.mod.uk/news/archive.cfm?storyid=6BC35053-1143-EC82-2EF5E68633B0006B |title=raf.mod.uk |publisher=raf.mod.uk |date=August 17, 2011 |accessdate=November 14, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091210213824/http://www.raf.mod.uk/news/archive.cfm?storyid=6BC35053-1143-EC82-2EF5E68633B0006B |archive-date=2009-12-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.theage.com.au/news/world/german-wwii-soldiers-get-proper-burial-after-60-years/2008/01/06/1199554485790.html | location=Melbourne Australia | work=The Age | first1=David | last1=Keys | title=German WWII soldiers get proper burial after 60 years | date=January 7, 2008 | accessdate=2014-01-17 | archive-date=2018-01-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180131143456/http://www.theage.com.au/news/world/german-wwii-soldiers-get-proper-burial-after-60-years/2008/01/06/1199554485790.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kokodaspirit.com/newsletters/kokoda-spirit-new-february%2027-2008.htm |title=kokodaspirit.com |publisher=kokodaspirit.com |accessdate=November 14, 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120309052120/http://www.kokodaspirit.com/newsletters/kokoda-spirit-new-february%2027-2008.htm |archivedate=2012年3月9日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mcquat.co.uk/las_unknown_german.htm |title=mcquat.co.uk |publisher=mcquat.co.uk |accessdate=November 14, 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120309052120/http://www.mcquat.co.uk/las_unknown_german.htm |archivedate=2012年3月9日 }}</ref>仅[[美軍|美軍]]在戰爭中就有78,750名任务中失踪人员，佔战争中405,399名战争中死亡军人的19%。<ref name="franklin-12">{{cite book | last=Franklin | first=H. Bruce | authorlink=H. Bruce Franklin | title=M.I.A., Or, Mythmaking in America | url=https://archive.org/details/miaormythmakingi0000fran | publisher=[[Rutgers_University_Press|Rutgers University Press]] | year=1993 | isbn=0-8135-2001-0}} pp. 12–13.</ref>1991-1993年间，{{Link-en|美國參議院戰俘及失蹤人員事務委員會|United States Senate Select Committee on POW/MIA Affairs}}就[[第二次世界大战|二战]]中失踪至今仍未能寻获尸体的军人作了一份报告。<ref name="report-exec"/>和一战中的任务中失踪人员一样，经常有二战中的任务中失踪人员的遗体被发现，绝大部分的发现纯是出于偶然（如由于建设作业），少部分是由专门的遗体搜寻活动发现的。<ref>{{cite web|author=USA |url=http://www.pubmedcentral.nih.gov/articlerender.fcgi?artid=2080560 |title=pubmedcentral.nih.gov |publisher=pubmedcentral.nih.gov |accessdate=November 14, 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://uk.youtube.com/watch?v=cw5T3TOdtEA&feature=related |title=uk.youtube.com |publisher=uk.youtube.com |accessdate=November 14, 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P1-86873154.html |title=highbeam.com |publisher=highbeam.com |accessdate=November 14, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140611025935/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P1-86873154.html |archive-date=2014-06-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://www.flickr.com/photos/jrwarden/2397059392/ flickr.com]{{dead link|date=November 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://englishrussia.com/2008/07/19/russian-digging |title=Russian Digging |publisher=English Russia |date=2008-07-19 |accessdate=2012-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022065242/http://englishrussia.com/2008/07/19/russian-digging/ |archive-date=2012-10-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>同样和一战的情况相似的是，在西欧的任务中失踪人员的遗体通常都是单个单个地，或至多两三个一起地被发现。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2131075/Remains-missing-Spitfire-pilot-feared-ditched-Channel-70-years-later-French-farmers-field--family-lay-rest-honours.html | location=London | work=Daily Mail | first=Anthony | last=Bond | title=Remains of missing Spitfire pilot feared to have ditched in the Channel found 70 years later in French farmer's field... and now his family can lay him to rest with full honours | accessdate=2014-01-17 | archive-date=2020-04-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200406031600/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2131075/Remains-missing-Spitfire-pilot-feared-ditched-Channel-70-years-later-French-farmers-field--family-lay-rest-honours.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==朝鲜战争==
据估计，[[朝鮮戰爭|朝鮮戰爭]]期間仅在[[朝韩非军事区|非军事区]]，就埋有一万三千名[[大韓民國國軍|韓國軍]]官兵和两千名美国官兵。<ref name="bbc-korean">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/7679697.stm |title=War remains sought in Korea's DMZ |publisher=BBC News |date=2008-10-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081023152956/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/7679697.stm |archivedate=2008-10-23 |accessdate=2014-01-16 }}</ref> 美国{{Link-en|聯合戰俘及失蹤人員統計司令部|Joint POW/MIA Accounting Command}}和韩国的类似机构一直在试图定位和确认两国的士兵遗体。<ref name="bbc-korean"/>

在美军中，有8,177名军人被列为任务中失踪者，占到了整场战争期间死亡军人的15%。<ref name="franklin-12">{{cite book | last=Franklin | first=H. Bruce | authorlink=H. Bruce Franklin | title=M.I.A., Or, Mythmaking in America | url=https://archive.org/details/miaormythmakingi0000fran | publisher=[[Rutgers_University_Press|Rutgers University Press]] | year=1993 | isbn=0-8135-2001-0}} pp. 12–13.</ref>1953年初联合国军司令[[詹姆斯·范佛里特|詹姆斯·范佛里特]]将军估计任务中失踪的军人有“相当大一部分”还活着。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=qnQKAAAAIBAJ&pg=5414,2382403|title=U.S. Demands All POWs Be Turned Over|page=1|date=August 8, 1953|work=Ellensburg Daily Record|accessdate=2014-01-16|archive-date=2017-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170323235434/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=qnQKAAAAIBAJ&pg=5414,2382403|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1991–1993年间{{Link-en|美國參議院戰俘及失蹤人員事務委員會|United States Senate Select Committee on POW/MIA Affairs}}就[[朝鲜战争|朝鲜战争]]中任务中失踪人员的问题作了一份报告。<ref name="report-exec">{{cite web | url=http://www.fas.org/irp/congress/1993_rpt/pow-exec.html | title=Executive Summary | work=Report of the Select Committee on POW/MIA Affairs | publisher=[[United_States_Senate|United States Senate]] | date=1993-01-13 | accessdate=2008-01-03 | archive-date=2012-01-27 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6510IXjUM?url=http://www.fas.org/irp/congress/1993_rpt/pow-exec.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

至于还经常有战争中任务失踪人员的遗体被发现确认。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.defenselink.mil/releases/release.aspx?releaseid=8713 |title=defenselink.mil |publisher=defenselink.mil |accessdate=November 14, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091130233017/http://www.defenselink.mil/releases/release.aspx?releaseid=8713 |archive-date=2009-11-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.defenselink.mil/releases/release.aspx?releaseid=11550 |title=defenselink.mil |publisher=defenselink.mil |accessdate=November 14, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091201003148/http://www.defenselink.mil/releases/release.aspx?releaseid=11550 |archive-date=2009-12-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

据美国国防部战俘/任务中失踪人员办公室的发布，2014年1月15时还有7896名任务中失踪人员的尸体未寻获。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dtic.mil/dpmo/korea/reports/documents/pmkor_una_all.pdf |title=DTIC Korean War Unaccounted For List By Last Name |format=PDF |accessdate=November 14, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140115235440/http://www.dtic.mil/dpmo/korea/reports/documents/pmkor_una_all.pdf |archive-date=2014-01-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

尽管合众国在53年就知道至少还有900名美国战俘被关押在北朝鲜而未被交换回国，它却没有公布这一点，历史学家认为这是因为美国民众将会要求设法让这些战俘回国。 1996年国防部宣布没有证据表明这些战俘中还有人活到今天。<ref>U.S. Knew in 1953 North Koreans Held American P.O.W.'s. New York Times,September 17, 1996 article. http://www.nytimes.com/1996/09/17/world/us-knew-in-1953-north-koreans-held-american-pow-s.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1996/09/17/world/us-knew-in-1953-north-koreans-held-american-pow-s.html |date=20130521142726 }}</ref>到2005年据信还有至少500名韩国战俘被滞留在北朝鲜境内。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2005/08/23/international/asia/23korea.html|title=Red Cross Officials to Discuss P.O.W.'s Still Alive in North Korea|author=James Brooke|work=New York Times|date=August 23, 2005|accessdate=2014-01-16|archive-date=2013-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130521133941/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/08/23/international/asia/23korea.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

一批[[澳大利亞國防軍|澳大利亞國防軍]]的军人遗体同样从未寻获。<ref>{{cite news |author=5 Minutes 10 Minutes <!-- // .tier-2 --> |url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/national-affairs/call-for-search-for-korea-mias/story-fn59niix-1225901330757 |title=theaustralian.com.au |work=The Australian |accessdate=November 14, 2011 |date=August 5, 2010 |archive-date=2010-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100811173043/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/national-affairs/call-for-search-for-korea-mias/story-fn59niix-1225901330757 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
==越南戰爭==
[[File:United_States_POW-MIA_flag.svg|thumb]]
1973年[[巴黎和平協定|巴黎和平協定]]簽署後，591名美國戰俘在返鄉行動中被遣返。美國將大約1,350名[[美軍|美軍]]列為戰俘或在作戰中失蹤，大約有1,200名美軍在行動中陣亡且屍體未找回<ref name="dpmo-hist">{{cite web | url=http://www.dtic.mil/dpmo/vietnamwar/vietnam_history.htm | title=Vietnam War Accounting History | publisher=[[Defense_Prisoner_of_War/Missing_Personnel_Office|Defense Prisoner of War/Missing Personnel Office]] | access-date=2008-11-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081117195507/http://www.dtic.mil/dpmo/vietnamwar/vietnam_history.htm | archive-date=November 17, 2008 | url-status=dead }}</ref>。到1990年代初，戰爭中下落不明的總數已減少到2,255人，占越戰美國陣亡軍人總數58,152人的不到4%<ref name="franklin-12"/>。

大約80%的失蹤人員是在[[越南民主共和國|北越]]或[[寮國|寮國]]上空被擊落的飛行員，通常是在偏遠的山脈、熱帶雨林或水域；其餘的通常在茂密叢林中混亂的戰鬥中消失<ref>{{cite news | url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F0CE1DE1E30F93BA25757C0A965958260 | title=Old M.I.A. Theory Is Given a New Life | author=Engelberg, Stephen |work=The New York Times | date=1993-04-18}}</ref>。對這些事件的調查包括確定涉案飛行員是否在被擊落中倖存下來，如果沒有，則努力尋找他們的遺體。POW/MIA活動家在推動美國政府改善解決失踪人員命運的努力方面發揮了作用，不過這方面的進展緩慢，直到1980年代中期，美國和越南之間的關係開始改善，並進行了更多的合作努力。1990年代中期美國與越南關係正常化是這一進程的高潮。

相當多的猜測和調查得出的理論是，這些人中有相當多的人被兩國共產主義軍隊俘虜為戰俘，並在1973年戰爭結束後為美國關押。MIA活動人士堅持認為，自那時以來，越南政府和每個美國政府都密謀隱瞞這些囚犯的存在。美國政府堅決否認囚犯被拋在後面，或已作出任何努力來掩蓋他們的存在。流行文化反映了“活囚”理論，最引人注目的是1985年的電影《藍波[[第一滴血|第一滴血]]》第二部分。幾項國會調查已經對這個問題進行了調查，最終形成了規模最大、最徹底的美國參議院戰俘/軍事情報局事務特別委員會，由參議員約翰克里、鮑勃史密斯和約翰麥凱恩領導的1991年至1993年。其一致結論認為“沒有令人信服的證據證明任何美國人仍然被囚禁在東南亞” <ref name="report-exec">{{cite web | url=https://fas.org/irp/congress/1993_rpt/pow-exec.html | title=Executive Summary | work=Report of the Select Committee on POW/MIA Affairs | publisher=[[United_States_Senate|United States Senate]] | date=1993-01-13 | access-date=2008-01-03}}</ref>。

還有大量來自北越和[[越南南方民族解放陣線|越共]]的失蹤軍人遺骸尚未找到。1974年，[[武元甲|武元甲]]將軍說他們有330,000人在作戰中失蹤<ref>{{cite book | last=Sorley | first=Lewis | title=A Better War: The Unexamined Victories and Final Tragedy of America's Last Years in Vietnam | publisher=[[Houghton_Mifflin_Harcourt|Houghton Mifflin Harcourt]] | year=2007 | isbn=978-0-15-601309-3}} p. 458.</ref>。截至1999年，失踪人數的估計通常約為 300,000。這個數字不包括從前[[越南共和國軍|南越武裝部隊]]中失踪的人，他們在越南政權下很少被考慮。越南政府沒有任何有組織的計劃來尋找自己的失踪人員，與它建立的尋找美國失踪人員的計劃相比。這種差異激怒了一些越南人。在2000年代，數以千計的越南人正在聘請通靈師尋找失踪家庭成員的遺骸。越南軍隊組織了它認為最好的通靈者，作為其超心理學力量的一部分，試圖尋找遺骸。此外，有時還會發現早期法國殖民時代的遺體：2009年1月，在河內市中心一個舊市場下的墳墓中發現了至少50名大約1946年至1947年間的反法抵抗戰士的遺體<ref>{{cite news | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/7828287.stm | title=Fighters found in Vietnam grave | author=Pham, Nga | work=BBC News | date=2009-01-14 | accessdate=2021-10-17 | archive-date=2021-10-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017161926/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/7828287.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

根據美國國防部戰俘/MIA會計機構的數據，截至2021年10月1日，仍有1,584名[[美軍|美軍]]和文職人員在[[越南|越南]]、[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]及[[寮國|寮國]]下落不明，[[遺體|遺體]]未被尋獲<ref name="ReferenceB"/>。

==海湾战争==
据美国[[国防部战俘/任务中失踪人员办公室|国防部战俘/任务中失踪人员办公室]]的发布，在[[海湾战争|沙漠风暴行动]]中有47名美国人被列为战俘/任务中失踪人员。<ref name="dtic.mil">[http://www.dtic.mil/dpmo/gulf_war/documents/IRAQI05B.pdf] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dtic.mil/dpmo/gulf_war/documents/IRAQI05B.pdf |date=20110629105924 }} ''Desert Storm Captives/Unaccounted-for'' Retrieved: December 14, 2010.</ref>到战争结束时美军确认了除一人外所有人的下落：21名战俘被遣返，23具遗体被发现，2具掉入海中并被确认为行动中阵亡尸体未收回（KIA-BNR）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dtic.mil/dpmo/Iraq_Conflicts/|title=Two KIA-BNR from Desert Storm Retrieved: December 14, 2010.|accessdate=2018-05-02|author=|date=|work=www.dtic.mil|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150131084110/http://www.dtic.mil/dpmo/Iraq_Conflicts/|archive-date=2015-01-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>仅有的未能确认者是美军少校[[lang-en|Michael Scott Speicher]]在他的[[F/A-18黃蜂式戰鬥攻擊機|F/A-18]]在战争第一晚被击落后被上报为失踪。<ref name="cnn-speicher">{{cite news | url=http://www.cnn.com/2003/US/04/23/sprj.irq.speicher.search/ | title=Initials may offer clue to missing Gulf War pilot | author=McIntire, Jamie | publisher=CNN | date=2003-04-23 | accessdate=2014-01-17 | archive-date=2020-12-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219225618/http://www.cnn.com/2003/US/04/23/sprj.irq.speicher.search/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>在之后数年中他的状态从失踪改为战死再改为失踪-被俘，也就是说他活着并被囚禁在伊拉克。2002年随着伊拉克战争的酝酿，他的下落越发为人所关心。[[华盛顿时报|华盛顿时报]]从3月到9月用了5次头版刊登关于他的文章。美国总统[[乔治·沃克·布什|小布什]]在一次对联合国大会的演讲中提到了Speicher。但到美军占领伊拉克后Speicher并未被发现他的下落也仍是个谜。<ref name="cnn-speicher"/><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5ieRx69tRJygBw63QD3HaV-ST_NBAD95JNIR81 | title=Panel calls for continuing probe of lost pilot | author=Evans, Ben | agency=Associated Press | date=2009-01-09}}</ref>最终在2009年8月他的遗体在沙漠中发现，当地人说他在坠地后马上就被埋葬了。<ref>{{cite press release | url=http://www.defenselink.mil/releases/release.aspx?releaseid=12862 | title=Remains Identified as Navy Captain Michael Scott Speicher | publisher=[[U.S._Department_of_Defense|U.S. Department of Defense]] | date=August 2, 2009 | access-date=2014-01-17 | archive-date=2009-12-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091202180921/http://www.defenselink.mil/releases/release.aspx?releaseid=12862 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.cnn.com/2009/US/08/02/us.gulf.war.remains/index.html | title=Remains found of first American shot down in Gulf War | publisher=CNN | date=August 2, 2009 | accessdate=2014-01-17 | archive-date=2019-07-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725212600/http://www.cnn.com/2009/US/08/02/us.gulf.war.remains/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>两名战死尸体未收回者为:<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dtic.mil/dpmo/Iraq_Conflicts/ |title=DPMO Accesed August 17, 2013 |access-date=2014-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227091728/http://www.dtic.mil/dpmo/Iraq_Conflicts/ |archive-date=2014-02-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
